{"title":"小城秋","authors":["于书恒"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":11,"day":16}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"小城秋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于书恒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一阵凉风，吹散了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几片落叶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可没能刮走"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满街的花裙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洒一场小雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋色更嫩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洗净了黎明，擦亮了黄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昏；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枫叶、菊花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给小城披金戴银。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小城的兴致不断更新，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"户里爱听乡音，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"偌多的阳台上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吊一小笼“童心”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蝈蝈——蝈蝈——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把城乡唱近。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里的秋季，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有个勇敢的海滨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海水凉了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个民族的体质"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却在升温，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这时的击浪者，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才是大海的主人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋临小城，谁也没留心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只感觉昼与夜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时间分得不匀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们用快镜头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把生活节奏理顺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车轮、机床、数字呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都往指标的尖上奔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"改革的年代，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才有诗眼画魂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一篇《秋色赋》，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"变成《小城春》……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}